{"tid":2102161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[水炮車mola]德法據報推動歐盟回應港區國安法　擬禁出口警務裝備","createTime":"2020-07-10T09:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T13:24:56.000Z","uid":51271,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"33722abfb53b32c48ddc5df4491a73df4b7fd756","tid":2102161,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:21:29.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》報道，法國及德國正推動歐盟採取措施，回應北京實施「港區國安法」，包括建議歐盟禁止向香港出口催淚彈及橡膠子彈等警務裝備、為逃避壓迫的香港政治人物，提供長期庇護，以及為更多香港學生提供獎學金。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，今次是法國與德國首次向歐盟提出針對「港區國安法」的應對措施，旨在支持香港公民社會，並非向中國實施制裁。歐盟外交官員透露，方案已得到其他歐盟成員國的支持，可能在下星期一的歐盟外長會議上討論。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩上月曾經警告，如果北京繼續推動「港區國安法」，將會面對非常負面的後果。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537013-20200710.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537013-20200710.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=7f606c72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537013-20200710.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=888ae1fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537013-20200710.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0bd434826d29978d5f8389b2b8a793223e75aa9a","tid":2102161,"uid":288913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"多多益善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625b9896cc19d20de5a764492da35c93f8131c20","tid":2102161,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"仁孚呢次仲唔仆街"},{"pid":"79a5f8cb523c5f1445ababf4c55b2fa88cada33c","tid":2102161,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T09:23:16.000Z","msg":"叫好過無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2221c709d130bd2cd4e1622